          <div class="accordion-details-panel">
            <p>We'll let you know upfront if you match the needs of a research study. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Integer posuere erat a ante venenatis.</p>
            <p><em>[Payment methods - PayID for Australians?]</em></p>
